commits.content:
:root
  margin 0
  background #372d4e

.approach-sec__topnav__item--active a
  color white !important

.map-sec__card
  // opacity 0.5
  // z-index unset

.map-sec__card::before
  position absolute
  content ''
  width calc(100% - 30px)
  height calc(100% - 30px)
  border-radius 16px
  top 60px
  left 60px
  z-index -1 !important
  border 3px solid #FFA756

.map__dot--active
  .map__dot__line
    opacity 1 !important
    width 1px !important
